channel.title: Miss Silabsoft, I Question You This
channel.description:
Hi, for anyone willing to answer these questions rep will be awarded, but here we go:
[ul][li]Why have we gone up in items, but my client crashes as soon as it hits a 377 item?[/li] [li]Is there any way to stop the music?[/li] [li]Why have you we got the next age in private servers yet chains and other items are still the old ones?[/li] [li]How and where did you get your cache re-compiler and how the did you create the items?[/li][/ul]
All i can think of at the moment, might come through with some more later =]
NOTE: these are not rants! just wondering why they are occurring, Miss Silabsoft, do not take this as offense thinking I'm saying "ooh your client ain't good enuugh i want moreeee" because I'm not, I'm proud i stuck with this community and didn't move onto others and am glad to see you trusted the community and have helped us all

item.title: Miss Silabsoft, I Question You This
item.dc:creator: @legend_rene legend rene
item.description:
@legend_rene wrote:

Why have we gone up in items, but my client crashes as soon as it hits a 377 item?
The client loads of MoparScape 3.2w/Aryan cache wich is 317 and does not support any 377 item.
Is there any way to stop the music?
Not unless silab disables it in her client or she releases a Open Source version of it. Or if you have vista you could try your sound settings and disable the Clients sounds.
Why have you we got the next age in private servers yet chains and other items are still the old ones?
Yet again , it loads of Moparscape cache , and it does not have the new models of Ahrims Armour , or Dragon Chainbody.
How and where did you get your cache re-compiler and how the did you create the items?
It is called a Repacker wich she has made herself , and she did not create the items , she added runescapes new models in place for some useless items , such as nulls.

Btw , don’t talk about rep++ if you don’t want a warn++.
